        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hongshulin/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4597403-6.jpg" alt="百盏" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34620547/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34620547/" class="">6</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hongshulin/" class=" " title="百盏">百盏</a>
                (自食其果。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34620547">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">

“行四百余里至睹货逻故国，国久空旷，城皆荒芜。从此东行六百余里至折摩驮那故国，即沮末地也，城廓岿然，人烟断绝，复此东北行千余里至纳缚波故国，即楼兰地也。”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-03-22 04:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“行四百余里至睹货逻故国，国久空旷，城皆荒芜。从此东行六百余里至折摩驮那故国，即沮末地也，城廓岿然，人烟断绝，复此东北行千余里至纳缚波故国，即楼兰地也。”
